title: Seated Dip Machine Plate Loaded- Tricep Dip Press Machine with Cable Bar for Biceps Chest Training, Hold up to 400LBS
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: [Versatile Upper Body Training Machine]- The seated triceps dip machine allows for focused and isolated workouts. Its convergent motion ensures that the triceps muscles are activated for maximum exercise effectiveness. In addition, the triceps press machine comes with a cable bar for doing biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls. It's a versatile machine that engages the muscles of the arms, shoulder and chest to take your upper body strength training to the next level!

[Improved Arms and Machine Design]- The seated dip machine is a safer and more effective alternative to traditional tricep dips, which can cause strain on the wrists and shoulders. With stable and controllable movements, this seated dip station minimizes the risk of injuries. Additionally, the tricep pushdown machine features a rotating handle that can be adjusted to fit varying shoulder widths, providing multiple grip options to target different areas of the triceps muscles.

[Personalized Adjustments]- It offers easy-to-use personalization adjustments, allowing you to customize your workout to suit your varying fitness levels and training goals with simple weight plate adjustments. Even beginners can experience challenging workouts without requiring extensive technical skills or coordination. The seat height and cable bar length can be adjusted to accommodate different body types, ensuring maximum comfort and efficiency during your exercise routine.

[High Quality Material]- The plate loaded tricep machine is composed of heavy-duty steel and premium coatings, making it durable and stable. The comfortable, sweat-resistant seat and backrest provide ample support for intense workouts and long-term use. Measuring only 42.7"x26.2"x51.2", it's the ideal size for any space in your home gym. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 LBS and compatibility with 1" and 2" weight plates, it can meet your most daily training needs. (Plates are not included)

[Easy to Use Step]- The tricep press machine is also featured by simplicity in use. To give your triceps a serious workout, all you need to do is choose the right weights, adjust the seat height, and grab onto the narrow handles. If you want to give your lower chest muscles some extra attention, just lean forward ever so slightly and switch to the wide handle. To perform a bicep curl, rise to your feet and plant them firmly on a rugged steel plate, then you can exercise freely with cable handle.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Increase your overall health & fitness with our Exercise Machine Cable Attachments | Be HulkFit! 
The problem with living a sedentary lifestyle and our solution | The benefits of a healthy lifestyle 
Your body and mind don't work at full capacity when you don't keep them occupied with a quality exercise routine. A quality workout not only makes your body stronger, but it makes your mind more resilient, builds your confidence, and improves your mental health. 
The Lat Pulldown Attachments are a functional piece of exercise equipment that is designed to give you a safe environment to exercise in and it will be a perfect addition to your home gym, garage gym, or light commercial setting. The multi-functional cable machine attachments will give you variety to your workout routine. You can complete multiple types of training that include: 
Strength training (Weightlifting tools include - barbell, weight plates, and dumbbells; helps with functional strength)
Circuit training (Example - 3 - 5 exercises performed in rotation; great for martial arts and other combat sports)
Station to station (3 - 5 sets of repetitions per exercise)
These exercise cable machine set allows you to perform exercises to help increase muscularity and overall fitness of your entire body, what we like to call your "Core 4", which includes: 
Arms (Example - tricep extensions)
Legs (Example - lateral leg raises)
Back (Example - lat pulldown)
Core (Example - cable crunches)
How we differ from the competition... 
Many competitors have released cable attachments for home gym set ups with fewer accessories. We responded by including more accessories, attachments, and carabiners. The package includes: 
(1) D Row
(1) Straight Bar
(1) Tricep Rope
(1) V Tricep Bar
(4) Carabiners
NOTE*** D Row, Straight Bar, Tricep Rope, and V Bar are also sold separately. 
Possibilities are endless with just a little bit of creativity! 
You can use these gym accessories with larger strength training equipment like the Cable Crossover, Lat Pulldown Machine, and Power Cage or Power Rack. All of these attachments will give you many more creative exercises to perform. Just use your imagination!

title: Titan Fitness Plate Loaded LAT Tower v2, Space Saving, Back, Shoulder
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Exercise Machine Parts & Accessories › Exercise Machine Attachments
description: The Plated-Loaded Lat Tower is a space-saving strength trainer designed to build your back and shoulder strength. This high-quality Lat Tower combines lat pull down and a low row position, making it a smart addition to any home gym. With dual, 13-inch loadable weight plate sleeves, you can slowly work up to higher intensity workouts with a weight capacity of up to 400-pounds. The tower comes with a Lat Bar, Low Row Handle, and Thigh Pads with four adjustable positions to accommodate athletes of all body types. Load up on plates and use lat pulldowns to efficiently target your upper body and back muscles to perform various pulldowns, bent-over rows, seated rows, and more.NOTE: Titan recommends bolting your Plate Loadable Lat Tower to the floor before performing upright cable rowsUPDATED VERSION: We added reinforcement braces between the seat and the main upright to increase the overall stability.FEATURES:- Compact, space-efficient trainer great for smaller spaces- Helps build your back and shoulder strength- Dual 13-inch weight posts fit Olympic weight plates- Four adjustable positions for the thigh pads will fit athletes of all body types- Four bolt-down holes give you the option for permanent mounting in your home or garage gym- Includes lat bar and low row handleSPECIFICATIONS:- Overall Height: 85-in.- Overall Depth: 57-in.- Overall Width: 47-in.- Loadable Sleeve Length: 13-in.- Lat Handle Length: 37.5-in.- Low Row Handle Length: 15-in.- Finish: Powder-Coated Black- Material: Steel- Weight Ratio: 1 to 1- Weight Capacity: 400 lb.- Product Weight: 120 lb.
features: BUILD YOUR ARMS AND BACK: Load up on plates and use lat pulldowns to target your upper body and back muscles, such as your latissimus dorsi. Switch to low rows or pushdowns to build out your biceps and triceps.

PERFECT FOR ATHLETES OF ALL SIZES: Our thigh pads have four different adjustable positions, to be sure we can accommodate athletes of all body types. The plate loadable feature gives fitness beginners the freedom to slowly work up to higher intensity workouts.

PERMANENT MOUNTING OPTION: Four bolt down holes are provided at the base frame of the lat tower, giving you the option to permanently mount this machine in your home or commercial gym. This is recommended before performing upright rows.
DURABLE STEEL CONSTRUCTION: The tough steel frame is designed to withstand a lifetime of intense workouts, and the sleek powder-coated paint will keep it looking fresh for years to come.

DIMENSIONS: This machine has an overall height of 85-inches, an overall depth of 57-inches, and the width measures 47-inches. Both weight sleeves provide 13-inches of loadable sleeve length. The Plate Loadable Lat Tower comes with the lat pull-down and low row handles.

breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Leg Machines
features: Commercial Grade for Home Gym & Garage Gym Use: Strong hamstrings and quadriceps are crucial for balance, speed and coordination. You'll wish every day was leg day with LIONSCOOL Leg Machine. Unique cable and pulley system supplies consistent resistance throughout the motions, which differs from traditional lever operated machine and assists with the growth of stronger and more defined muscles. It can be used for seated leg extension and lying leg curl. Only seated leg curl is not applicable.

Ultra Robust Structure with Rectangular Base and Extra Wide Foot Pads: The whole machine is constructed with 14-gauge tube and purpose built on a creative rectangular base to distribute pressure and eliminate rocking, ensuring an outstanding 400LBS weight plate loading capacity. And the weight capacity for users can reach up to 1000LBS. Each base foot has an enlarged stepped plate with a solid rubber covering, which increases stability further.

Tough Cable and Pulley Handle Great Weights: The steel cable is 8mm thick and will last through grueling workouts. We specially design an adjustable bolt to regulate tension in case the cable stretches out over the years. The pulley with an enhanced steel core can withstand heavier loads and more intensive training. Plate loading post measures 12” and fits 2-inch weight plates smoothly with its hard chrome plated surface.

Extreme Convenient with Open Seat and Adjustable Pads: We discard the impractical knee holder to make getting in and off the machine effortless and smooth. 6 seat depth adjustable backrest will accommodate users of all heights. Our self-adjusting foot roller with its 7 angles adjustable arm will conform to your leg position freely and the seat is quickly adjustable by one pull pin between seated and prone positions.

Innovative Seat Structure and Feel Comfort in Details: We have unique three-segment seat structure to maximize your comfort during your lying leg curls. The seat pad, middle pad and the backrest as well as the foam foot roller, are all 2.2” thick with high density EPE foam, combining firm support with gentle feel. All cushions feature textured PU surface to ensure anti-slip performance. And two pairs of rubber grip handles located on both sides help assist body stability.

Awesome Addition to Home Gym with Reliable Warranty: The assembled dimension is 45” width x 56” depth x 41” height to fit into your home gym. We offer Manufacturer Limited Warranty: 2 years on framework (structural steel & welds) and 1 year on other parts. Assembly instructions and wrenches will come with the machine. aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
A BETTER INDOOR ROWING EXPERIENCE 
When you're on your concept 2 rower, you want to feel good. You want to experience the burn in your lungs as you push then pull back. You want to fall into the rhythm of the machine as you glide back and front. What you don't want is distracting butt and back pains as you rack up the meters on the machine. Combine this cushion with rowing gloves, and you are ready to row for hours. This cushion measures 12.5" x 9.75" x 0.63". 
ABOUT HORNET WATERSPORTS ROWING SEAT CUSHIONS 
Our seatpads for the concept 2 rowing machine are designed for athletes of all skill levels. Whether you're a regular at your gym or you're just starting your in-home training program, this cushion can help you feel your best throughout your workouts - even multiple rowing sessions a day. You can use it at your home gym, rowing club, Crossfit box, or anywhere that you use a concept two erg rowing machine. 
OTHER ROWING MACHINES 
Our pads will fit on most indoor exercise rowing machines. The brands include but are not limited to Hydrow, WaterRower, NordicTrack RW Rower, Stamina, SunnyD and Sunny Health and Fitness, the various C2 machine, and more. 
NOT JUST FOR ROWING, BUT ALSO CAN BE USED FOR MANY OUTDOOR ACTIVITIES 
Because this new cushion is bigger and thicker, you can use it for many outdoor activities such as fishing, tailgating, watching baseball, basketball, football, soccer, hockey and many other sports. It can also be used when on your kayak, canoe, or small vessel or boat. 
BRING IT TO YOUR GYM 
Bring your cushion with you to your local gym in your gym bag along with your other exercise accessories. You can learn more about Hornet Watersports rowing products. Our complete line also includes rowing gloves, rowing machine covers, and more.

title: Body-Solid Pro Clubline (LVSR) Leverage Seated Row Machine - Unilateral Dual-Axis, Adjustable Gas-Assisted Chest Support, 360-Degree Grips

breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Home Gym Systems
description: The Body-Solid Leverage Seated Row Machine (LVSR) helps users build depth in the middle back and train the lower lats with biomechanically-correct movements. Featuring dual-axis diverging arms, this rowing machine lets each arm move independently, with sealed bearing pivot points for smooth, uninterrupted movement. 360-degree articulating hand grips provide a natural range of motion while you pull, while the gas-assisted chest support delivers total isolation of back muscles while supporting users of various arm lengths. Made with a heavy-duty 2 by 3-inch 11-gauge steel mainframe and double-stitched upholstery, this seated row machine is durably constructed to stand up to rigorous use in gyms and clubs. It uses Olympic weight plates for resistance (weight plates sold separately). When assembled, the Body-Solid Leverage Seated Row Machine measures 65 by 35 by 44 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 158 pounds. It is backed by the Body-Solid Lifetime In-Home Warranty and Full Commercial Warranty.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

OPTIMIZED FOR PERFORMANCE: With its gas-assisted chest support and adjustable seat pad, it caters to users of varying heights and arm lengths, enabling a personalized and isolated back-strengthening experience. The 360-degree articulating hand grips allow for a natural range of motion, reducing the risk of injury while maximizing muscle engagement for a more efficient rowing motion.

BIO-MECHANICALLY ENGINEERED: Designed with dual-axis, unilateral, diverging-arm movement to emulate a natural rowing action. This advanced design ensures a full range of motion, targeting the intricate muscles of the back for a comprehensive workout, and promoting symmetrical strength development.

SUITABLE FOR ALL FITNESS LEVELS: The Seated Row Machine stands as a cornerstone in home and commercial gyms alike, tailored to cater to a broad spectrum of user abilities. Featuring an intuitive leverage system, it effortlessly adapts to various weight adjustments, catering to individuals at every stage of their fitness journey, from novice to elite athletes.

DIMENSIONS: Engineered with a robust 2" x 3" 11-gauge steel mainframe and electrostatically applied metallic silver powder coat paint finish, ensuring durability and resistance to wear and tear. Measures 65"x35"x44" and weighs 158lbs.

title: Titan Fitness Plate-Loaded Chest Supported T-Bar Row Machine, 400 LB Capacity, Incline Back Strength Training Machine with Adjustable Diamond-Textured Footplate and Multi-Grip Handles
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness
description: The Chest Support Row is a leverage machine designed to isolate and target your back muscles, biceps, lats, and shoulders while reducing strain on your lower back. It provides a stable and supported platform for performing a rowing motion while keeping your back straight and core engaged. Start by adjusting the diamond-textured footplate so that your chest is comfortably supported against the chest pad when you lean forward, ensuring that your upper body is stable and supported. Load up to 400 LB Olympic-sized bumper plates onto the 13.5" long weighted sleeve. Grasp either vertical or horizontal grip handles and pull the handlebar towards your upper abdomen or lower chest, squeezing your shoulder blades together as you perform the rowing motion. Build the back you have always wanted and take your workout to a new level with the Plate-Loaded Chest Support T-Bar Row Machine.FEATURES:- Perform T-Bar Rows, Chest-Supported Rows, Single-Arm Rows, Wide/Narrow-Grip Rows- Adjustable, stationary, vertical and horizontal grip handles with a durable rubber grip- Adjustable pop-pin style diamond plated non-slip footplate- Weight post sleeve fits Olympic-sized weight plates- High-quality vinyl incline chest pad- Includes holes for bolting the machine to the floorSPECIFICATIONS: - Overall Height: 50-in.- Overall Width: 43-in.- Overall Depth: 84-in.- Chest Pad: 20-in. x 10-in.- Footplate: 23.5-in. x 17.5-in.- Weight Sleeve Length: 14.5-in.- Weight Sleeve Diameter: 50mm- Vertical Grip Length: 9-in. - Vertical Grip Spread: 17.5-in. - Horizontal Grip Length: 5.5-in. - Horizontal Grip Spread: 26-in.- Grip Diameter: 31mm- Finish: Powder-Coated Black- Material : 11-Ga Steel- User Height Range: 4'-11" to 6'-6"- User Weight Capacity: 265 lb.- Rowing Weight Capacity: 400 lb.- Product Weight: 100 lb.
features: ADJUSTABLE SETTINGS: Designed to accommodate users of different heights and body types, this Plate-Loaded T-bar Row Machine features an adjustable diamond textured footplate and five set positions for the multi-grip style handles.

CHEST SUPPORT: The non-slip, sweat-resistant incline chest pad design provides additional stability and reduces back pressure, while the wide and narrow grip handles allow for focused training of the upper and middle back muscles, helping to increase strength and size.

UPPER BODY TRAINING: The multi-grip (horizontal and vertical) row bar simultaneously works multiple muscle groups, including the back, shoulders, arms, and core, effectively improving overall strength, stability, and coordination of the body.

DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: The frame is built with a sturdy, solid steel construction that keeps this machine dependable and long-lasting through even the highest intensity workouts. The machine fits Olympic-sized weight plates that will hold up to 400 LB weight capacity.

What type of pulley handle is on this rower? 
The SF-RW5515 features a durable nylon pulley. Pulley line is flat and provides a smooth and quiet pull with each row. 
How high does the seat sit from the ground? 
The cushioned seat measures 10.1 inches at its lowest and max 11.7 inches, making it easy to get on/off the machine. 
Is this machine easy to pack away to save space when not in use? Does it fold up by chance? 
Yes, there's a pin that you can remove to fold it in half, the sliderail will fold upward. Reinsert the pin to secure. Wheels at the front of the unit make it easily portable for storing. 
What type of pedals does the rower have?

features: HEAVY DUTY BACK ROW MACHINE: It is constructed with 2"x 2" 12-gauge steel for strength and durability, and high-density dual-layered padding to last through your most intense back workout. Product Description
Plate Loaded Seated Rowing Back Machine – Premium Back Strengthening and Muscle Development for Home and Commercial Gyms 
Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine with Independent Arm Movements for Targeted Back and Bicep Development 
Break free from conventional rowing machines with our Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine featuring independent arms. This innovative design allows for simultaneous or alternating workouts, ensuring balanced back development and equal attention to both sides. Perfect for targeting lats, middle back, and biceps, this machine enhances your muscle development and strength training. Whether you’re training for endurance or building muscle, the independent arm movement provides a superior, personalized workout experience. Ideal for home gyms or commercial gym setups, this seated row machine is designed to improve back strength and overall upper body performance. Maximize your workout efficiency and achieve your fitness goals faster with this advanced feature. 
Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine with Rotating Hand Grips for Improved Back and Bicep Workouts 
In addition to the stationary grip handle that mimics the function of a T Row Machine, this Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine features a rotating grip handle for enhanced movement. This crucial design ensures natural arm movement during each row, minimizing elbow strain and promoting proper form. Ideal for muscle rehabilitation and physical therapy exercises, the rotating grip helps reduce stress on the joints while effectively targeting the lats, middle back, and biceps. Whether you're recovering from an injury or seeking to enhance overall strength, this feature ensures a comfortable and efficient workout experience. Perfect for users at any fitness level, this seated row machine is an excellent choice for both strength training and rehabilitation exercises. 
Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine with Rotating Hand Grips and Space-Saving Storage Design 
Versatility at its peak, the Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine is designed to accommodate both standard and Olympic-sized weights, allowing you to easily adjust the load for your workout. The package includes 2 Olympic sleeve adapters and clips for seamless switching between standard and Olympic plates. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 pounds, this machine is built to handle even the most intense workouts. Whether you're lifting heavy for strength training or performing lighter sets for muscle endurance, this row machine offers unmatched flexibility to meet your fitness needs. Perfect for home gyms or commercial setups, it’s a powerful tool for both muscle development and weight training. 
The seated rowing machine is an excellent choice for strengthening your back muscles, specifically the middle back and latissimus dorsi (lats), which are crucial for everyday movement and lifting. As an added benefit, biceps are engaged in the pulling motion, giving you a comprehensive workout that improves upper body strength. This plate loaded rowing machine is designed to help you achieve balanced muscle development in one effective machine, from the upper back to the arms. 
Built with heavy-duty steel, this rowing machine offers durability and longevity for both home and light-commercial gym use. It features thick steel construction with a 12-gauge steel frame to ensure it can handle heavy weight loads. The machine also includes rubber end caps, which prevent floor damage and provide stability during the most intense workouts. 
Unlike traditional rowing machines, this seated row machine features independent arms that allow for both simultaneous and alternating workouts. This unique design ensures that each side of your back receives equal attention, promoting balanced muscle development and helping to improve your posture and symmetry. 
This machine is equipped with multi-dimensional grip handles for a variety of training options. The stationary grip mimics the function of a traditional T Row Machine, while the rotating grip handle ensures a natural arm movement during each pull. By reducing strain on your elbows and improving your form, this feature makes your workouts more effective and comfortable. 
The Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine offers exceptional adjustability to accommodate users of all sizes and fitness levels. The 4-position adjustable seat pad and 5-position adjustable chest pad allow for a customized fit, while the tapered seat ensures maximum comfort throughout your rowing sessions. Whether you’re training for strength or endurance, you’ll be able to adjust the machine to your preferred position and achieve the best results. 
Designed for versatility, this rowing machine can hold both standard and Olympic-sized plates. With the included 2 Olympic sleeve adapters and weight clips, you can easily switch between weights, ensuring that your workouts are always challenging and progressive. Plate loaded systems allow for easy adjustments, making it ideal for those looking to push their limits in muscle development. 
This seated row machine is capable of supporting up to 200 lbs. per arm, for a total weight load of 400 lbs., making it perfect for even the most demanding lifting routines. Whether you're focusing on high-rep endurance sets or heavy lifting for muscle mass, this machine can handle it all. 
Designed with both home gym users and light-commercial gym settings in mind, the Plate Loaded Seated Row Machine is the perfect piece of equipment for anyone looking to strengthen and define their back muscles. With its sturdy design and versatile features, it’s an investment that will take your fitness to the next level. 
Durable Construction: Crafted from 12-gauge steel, this machine is built for long-term use, with a solid weight capacity of up to 400 lbs.
Independent Arms: Achieve even muscle development with independent arm movement for balanced back training.
Adjustable Comfort: Features a 4-position adjustable seat and 5-position chest pad for personalized workouts and optimal comfort.
Multi-Dimensional Grip: The rotating grip handle ensures proper form, minimizing elbow strain during rowing exercises.
Plate Loaded Design: Holds standard and Olympic-sized weights for added versatility and progression.
Versatile and Effective: Perfect for muscle development, including back, lats, biceps, and overall upper body strength.

Take Your Workouts to the Next Level with the Valor Fitness Lat Pulldown Machine 
Transform Your Home Gym with the Valor Fitness Lat Pulldown Machine 
Looking to enhance your home gym setup and achieve professional-level workouts? The Valor Fitness Lat Pulldown Machine is the ultimate solution for strength training enthusiasts seeking versatility, durability, and performance. Built with a heavy-duty 2" x 2" 12-gauge steel frame, this machine is designed to handle the most intense training sessions while providing the functionality you need for a full-body workout. 
Whether you’re focused on building upper body strength, toning your arms and shoulders, or improving core stability, this multi-functional cable machine is your perfect fitness companion.

title: Mikolo Seated Dip Machine, Plate Loaded Tricep Machine Home Gym, with Cable Bar for Biceps Chest Training, 400LBS Capacity
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weight Machines › Upper Body Machines
features: [Versatile Upper Body Training Machine]- The seated triceps dip machine allows for focused and isolated workouts. Its convergent motion ensures that the triceps muscles are activated for maximum exercise effectiveness. In addition, the triceps press machine comes with a cable bar for doing biceps exercises like upright cable rows and biceps curls. It's a versatile machine that engages the muscles of the arms, shoulder and chest to take your upper body strength training to the next level!

[Improved Arms and Machine Design]- The seated dip machine is a safer and more effective alternative to traditional tricep dips, which can cause strain on the wrists and shoulders. With stable and controllable movements, this seated dip station minimizes the risk of injuries. Additionally, the tricep pushdown machine features a rotating handle that can be adjusted to fit varying shoulder widths, providing multiple grip options to target different areas of the triceps muscles.

[Personalized Adjustments]- It offers easy-to-use personalization adjustments, allowing you to customize your workout to suit your varying fitness levels and training goals with simple weight plate adjustments. Even beginners can experience challenging workouts without requiring extensive technical skills or coordination. The seat height and cable bar length can be adjusted to accommodate different body types, ensuring maximum comfort and efficiency during your exercise routine.

[High Quality Material]- The plate loaded tricep machine is composed of heavy-duty steel and premium coatings, making it durable and stable. The comfortable, sweat-resistant seat and backrest provide ample support for intense workouts and long-term use. Measuring only 42.7"x26.2"x51.2", it's the ideal size for any space in your home gym. With a maximum weight capacity of 400 LBS and compatibility with 1" and 2" weight plates, it can meet your most daily training needs. (Plates are not included)

[Easy to Use Step]- The tricep press machine is also featured by simplicity in use. To give your triceps a serious workout, all you need to do is choose the right weights, adjust the seat height, and grab onto the narrow handles. If you want to give your lower chest muscles some extra attention, just lean forward ever so slightly and switch to the wide handle. To perform a bicep curl, rise to your feet and plant them firmly on a rugged steel plate, then you can exercise freely with cable handle.

modules.text:
Rowing on the open water provides a dynamic, adaptive workout that helps you burn calories, tone the entire body, improve posture and more. Bring the benefits of water rowing into the comfort of home with the Stamina Wave Water Rower 1435. This Rower combines a carefully-designed combination of performance-oriented features and comfort elements to drive results. 
This rowing machine provides an effective strength-building workout that’s great for the whole body.

features: 【OPTIMIZED MOTION】: Easily sculpt a V-shaped back with our seated row machine! Replicate the traditional pulling movement towards the chest, it's ergonomically designed to follow the body's natural motion, ensuring maximum engagement and a full range of motion. Feel the intensity as your back muscles engage, supported by smooth-operating bearings for a seamless exercise experience. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned pro, mastering this back machine is effortless.

【COMMERCIAL-GRADE MACHINE】: Upgrade to a commercial-grade fitness equipment at an affordable price! With dimensions of 58.2" x 42" x 55.9", our seated row machine plate loaded offers generous space for fluid movement. Crafted from heavy-duty 13-gauge steel, its sturdy frame supports up to 600lbs, guaranteeing stability during rigorous workouts. Plus, its extended 9.6" weight holder effortlessly holds four 35lbs weights. Experience durability, stability, and convenience all in one machine.

【MULTIPLE GRIP HANDLES】: Featuring multiple grip handles that cater to every inch of your back, this leverage seated row machine allows you to effortlessly target various muscle groups with ease.The narrow grips for lats and mid back, while wider grips can target your upper back and delts, you can customize your workout for optimal results. Plus, our non-slip coated handles ensure comfort and safety throughout the workouts.

【INDEPENDENT ARMS】: Back machine’s independent mechanical arms grant you the flexibility to alternate sides or engage both simultaneously. This versatility makes the lat machine particularly advantageous for people aiming to balance unilateral strength. By adjusting the weights, customize your exercises to target specific areas effectively. Moreover, the inclusion of an Assist Handle offers additional support during single-arm exercises, promoting proper form and amplifying your results.

【COMFORT& ADJUSTABILITY】: Boasting an extra-thick seat and chest cushion for optimal comfort during intense sessions. Adjustable in four positions to suit different body types, the back row machine seamlessly transitions to a standing row with a quick-detach seat, maximizing muscle engagement. Non-slip foot pedals ensure stability and effective upper body isolation. Experience the pinnacle of seated rowing, where comfort, adjustability, and performance converge effortlessly.

features: FULL-BODY WORKOUT: This rowing machine uses an extended rail design to effectively work multiple muscle groups in the legs, buttocks, core, back, arms, and shoulders. Whether you are a beginner or a fitness expert, rowing can stimulate your potential and make you become stronger.

EFFICIENT DIGITAL MONITORING: The digital monitor function is very practical, which can display important data such as time, calories, and number of strokes, so that you can know your physical condition during exercise. With real-time feedback, you can make adjustments based on the data and improve the efficiency of each exercise.

STURDY & DURABLE STRUCTURE: This rower machine is suitable for daily exercise at home, with a load capacity of up to 350 pounds, ensuring stability even for long-term use. The sturdy track system ensures safety and stability, while the curved drive system minimizes wear and tear and extends the life of the rowing machine.

EASY ASSEMBLY & MOVEMENT: The design of easy disassembly and assembly allows you to move flexibly at any time, suitable for use in different spaces at home. Equipped with two wheels at the front, you can easily move this fitness rowing machine by just lifting the rear end. Absolutely! It’s designed for a full-body workout that includes squats, rowing motions, and other exercises to engage multiple muscle groups. 
Does the Row-N-Ride machine require electricity to operate? 
No, this machine is manually operated and does not require electricity. 
Which muscle groups does this exerciser target? 
This machine primarily targets the glutes, thighs, and core, while also engaging the arms and shoulders during the rowing motion for a full-body workout. 
Is the machine foldable for convenient storage? 
Yes, the machine is foldable, making it easy to store away when not in use—perfect for saving space at home.
